Right, but previously when I did something like:

```js
/* Camper Code */
function goToStore() {
  const location = store;
}
```

```js
/* Tests */
assert.match(goToStore.toString(), /const\s+location/);
```

The test would fail, because `const` was transpiled to `var`.
